## CLAUDE.md Hierarchy

Configuration cascades from global to specific:

```
1. ~/.claude/CLAUDE.md          ← Global coding standards (all projects)
2. .claude/CLAUDE.md            ← Workspace config (this folder's .claude)
3. CLAUDE.md                    ← THIS FILE (workspace root)
4. _meta.notes/CLAUDE.md        ← Obsidian vault guidelines
5. <project>/CLAUDE.md          ← Project-specific rules
6. <project>/src/*/CLAUDE.md    ← Folder-specific patterns
```

**Each project has its own CLAUDE.md** with:
- Tech stack details
- File organization
- Coding patterns
- Testing requirements
- Deployment procedures

